{"type": "article", "id": 29512, "title": "咖啡包装", "description": "", "date": "2016-07-12T23:01:53Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 41, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160712233740dwgkZiGahtRsbzWp.jpeg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>看到包装上稀奇古怪的象形文字时，你或许还以为这是一个来自非洲的咖啡品牌，实际上这是 <a href=\"http://goodapples.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Good Apples</a> 为呈现美国科罗拉多州咖啡品牌 OZO 多达 15 种以上的咖啡豆而专门设计的一套文字体系和对应的排版规则。这种富有趣味的系统不仅方便顾客挑选出自己心仪的咖啡豆，也普及了每一款咖啡豆的背景资料。Good Apples 还将咖啡豆分为三种大类，分别对应蓝绿红三种颜色，让包装显得更加生动活泼。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160712233759C0Y8dDHJWpaLw2V1.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.417000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160712233800fGKbuH0WLysZClhc.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.719000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160712233800QjEA61FcOdUT9g2S.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.417000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}